  "text": "The Prostate Cancer Clinical Trials Working Group 2 (PCWG2) defines the following criteria [CITATION_1] : serum castration levels of testosterone (testosterone \\50 ng/dL or \\1.7 nmol/L), PSA progression and/or clinical progression to castration. Anti-androgen withdrawal for at least 4-6 weeks is recommended before considering the diagnosis of CRPC.",
